      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i was prescribed some antibiotics for a nasty skin infection i had last week. i've been taking them for 3 days now and the redness and swelling are basically gone. i feel totally fine. is it okay if i just stop taking them now since the infection seems cleared up? i don't really want to keep putting chemicals in my body if i don't need to.",
