      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it feels like a lot of unnecessary medicine. like, if the bacteria are already gone, why keep killing more of them? it just seems like it's harder on my stomach and liver for no reason. are you sure it's actually necessary to finish all 10 days if there's clearly no sign of infection left?",
