    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't see why the risk of \"resistance\" is so high for just one small skin thing. if i stop now, i'm basically just avoiding unnecessary side effects. wouldn't it be more logical to just monitor it, and if it comes back, then i take more? it feels like doctors just over-prescribe to be safe, but i'd rather just trust my own body since it's already healed.",
